{"openapi":"3.0.3","info":{"title":"Spotify Data API","description":"Authenticated proxy to the Spotify Data API.\n\nAll `/spotify-data/*` endpoints require a valid API key sent in the\n`x-rapidapi-key` header. `/docs`, `/openapi.json`, `/openapi.yaml`,\nand `/help` are public.\n\n### Concert endpoints\n\n- `/partner/concert-locations` → search cities/venues, returns `geoHash` + `geonameId`.\n- `/partner/concert-feed` → list concerts in an area (paginated). Optional deep-search via `details=true`.\n- `/partner/concert` → full concert details by ID/URI/URL (lineup, tickets, venue).\n- `/partner/artist-concerts` → upcoming concerts for an artist.\n- `/partner/search-concert-artists` → resolve artist by name → upcoming concerts in one call.\n\nConcert endpoints accept `details=true` (parallel deep-fetch, capped by `detailsLimit`,\nmax 50) and `parsed=true` (flat normalized response shape).\n","version":"1.1.0","contact":{"name":"API Support"}},"servers":[{"url":"/spotify-data","description":"Proxy server"}],"security":[{"ApiKeyAuth":[]}],"tags":[{"name":"Health"},{"name":"Search"},{"name":"Albums"},{"name":"Artists"},{"name":"Tracks"},{"name":"Playlists"},{"name":"Users"},{"name":"Charts"},{"name":"Downloads"},{"name":"Partner"},{"name":"Concerts"},{"name":"Browse"},{"name":"Audiobooks"},{"name":"Shows"},{"name":"Episodes"},{"name":"Markets"},{"name":"Lookups"},{"name":"Batch"},{"name":"Analysis"},{"name":"Snapshots"},{"name":"Webhooks"},{"name":"Cache"},{"name":"Tracking"},{"name":"AI"},{"name":"Credentials"}],"components":{"securitySchemes":{"ApiKeyAuth":{"type":"apiKey","in":"header","name":"x-rapidapi-key"}},"schemas":{"Error":{"type":"object","properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean"},"error":{"type":"string"},"message":{"type":"string"}}},"SuccessEnvelope":{"type":"object","properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean"},"data":{"description":"Endpoint payload (raw upstream or parsed shape)."},"metadata":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":true}}}},"parameters":{"O